          </itemmetadata>
          <presentation>
            <material>
              <mattext texttype="text/html">&lt;p&gt;What&amp;#x27;s the result? `const card = document.querySelector(&amp;#x27;.card&amp;#x27;); card.style.transition = &amp;#x27;all 0.3s&amp;#x27;; card.style.transform = &amp;#x27;scale(1.5)&amp;#x27;;`&lt;/p&gt;</mattext>
